      • disassociateDeadNodes

        public static ClusterState disassociateDeadNodes​(ClusterState clusterState)
        Unassign any persistent tasks executing on nodes that are no longer in the cluster. If the task's assigment has a non-null executor node and that node is no longer in the cluster then the assignment is set to LOST_NODE_ASSIGNMENT
        参数:
        clusterState - The clusterstate
        返回:
        If no changes the argument clusterState is returned else a copy with the modified tasks
